BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:WGpQ4PgB8Ah755clHWIdq
SUMMARY:Old Mervs\, guests
DTSTAMP:20260401T021322Z
DTSTART:20260524T033000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $25 ($31.68 after fees)\n\nDay of: $30 ($36.83 after f
	ees)\n\nOld Mervs:\n\nAn unbreakable bond shared between lifelong mates\, 
	Dave and Henry hail from the tiny farming community of Kojonup\, a town th
	ree hours south of Perth\, Western Australia.\n\nStarting out as school fr
	iends and rehearsing in a makeshift space in an old farm shed\, Old Mervs 
	are a far cry from their humble beginnings.\n\nRiding a wave of wins\, Old
	 Mervs are celebrating a massive 2025 after the success of their ARIA-char
	ting debut album release and sold out tours across Australia\, the United 
	States\, the UK and Europe.\n\nRecorded with ARIA award-winning producer C
	hris Collins\, their debut self-titled album scored coveted Australian you
	th broadcaster triple j’s Feature Album of the week and landed at #1 on th
	e ARIA album charts\, winning hearts with hits “Parched“\, “What You’ve Lo
	st”\, “Forget It”\, “Everyone Will See It” and “Don’t Go”.\n\nIn 2025\, th
	e pair embarked on a mammoth 20 date album tour across Australia and New Z
	ealand along with their biggest headline home-state show to date at Perth 
	HPC. They then headed to the US to play at world-renowned festival Lollapa
	looza alongside names like Olivia Rodrigo\, Tyler the Creator and Sabrina 
	Carpenter\, bookended by a massive run of headline shows across the States
	\, stopping in for a Audiotree session too. They closed out the year with 
	a return to the UK and their first ever shows in Europe.\n\nThis year look
	s to be just as big\, if not bigger. With new music in the pipeline\, and 
	a stack of touring at home and across the globe\, Old Mervs are thrilled t
	o return to the US again for a stack of huge headline shows\, along with K
	ilby Block Party\, Gov Ball and more dates to be announced!\n\nPlease note
	\, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+ bar and venue and does not accept v
	ertical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/R92dc6b0f417\n\nFrom Sunse
	t Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/R92dc6b0f417
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
